<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>SWEET HOUR PRAYER</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Paucham phat nuom, paucham phat nuom,
 Khawvel buoina apat ei sam;
 Ka Pa chutphah ma-ah ei sawl,
 Taksap leh deihcheng ngen dingin,
 Lungkham leh lungzin lai inle;
 Ka thagau in muonna a mui,
 * Thempa thang chuh ka peltha zel;
 Nangmah ziekin, paucham phat nuom! (2)

[V2]
 2. Paucham phat nuom, paucham phat nuom!
 Na tha ten ka ngetna puon tin;
 Thagau amah ngakte thudik,
 Ginum a vang piepa kawmah;
 A mel hawl dingin ei sawla;
 A thu leh hehpihna pawm di'n,
 * Ka buoina Amah ah ngang ka;
 Hun ngak ing ka, paucham phat nuom! (2)

[V3]
 3. Paucham phat nuom, paucham phat nuom!
 Na lungmuonna chun ei nem in;
 Pisgah tangsip ah ka thil a,
 Ka In lam zuona ka chieh man;
 Taksa thil nusien chieh ingting,
 Kumsawt a kipahman chang din;
 * Kiko in van lam ah leng ka,
 &quot;Mangpha, mangpha, paucham phat nuom! (2)</lyrics>
<hymn_number>339</hymn_number>
</song>